ttml2srt - Timed Text Markup Language to SubRip converter

I maintain this in order to obtain subtitles in an omxplayer-compatible
format from NRK Nett-TV (tv.nrk.no). For now it is just a quick hack
that has not been extensively tested.

Installation:
  autoreconf --install
  ./configure --prefix=$HOME/.local
  make all install clean

Usage:
  ttml2srt [-o OUTPUT] [INPUT]

Options:
  -h, --help             Prints help message
  --version              Prints version
  -o, --output=FILENAME  Specifies output file
